dct_title_s: Flemmings Spezialkarte für den Deutsch-Französisch-Belgischen Krieg
dct_alternative_sm: Flemings special map for the German-French-Belgian War
dct_description_sm: Shows frontlines at the start of March 1917 and the end of April 1917.
Also roads, railroads, monasteries, churches/chapels, ruines, mines, villages, cities and towns.
